title: Playpen Revenge
author: Lord_Magmus
pages:
#- Playpen Revenge§0
§0-------------------§0
§0A sequel of sorts to Reasoning with Titan and Phila1823§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0-------------------By Magmus
#- When I found out about the attack on the Playpen vault during the Titan War, I decided foolishly to observe the fight. I brought some weak armour and a diamond sword, and shouted out in chat about being a non-combatant. I was soon pearled by
#- AgentExtortion AKA Celoxia, freed, and killed. I respawned back in my house in Iria. I was later told by Wolfeyes391 that there was a plan to attack Titan while everyone was away trying to break the Playpen vault. Wolf later warned that it was too
#- dangerous, but I didn't listen. I travelled down the rails to Titan, and just before I could break a bastion, the Titan forces were alerted to my presence. I quickly panicked and travelled down the rails back to Carbon, and on the rails ecountered 
#- Folters. We had a conversation for a bit about "Friendship Trees" until Folters started joking about being Hantzu's alt. I panicked, and was afraid I would have to fight him in Carbon. I did not. However, the things he was saying inspired me to return to
#- Playpen, dispite multiple factors such as my gear being unenchanted diamond, my low skill at PVP and the fact that "Peaceful noncombatat" would be an easy excuse to sneak up and pearl people. As one would expect, Celoxia pearled me again.
#- This time, I was in the end for a much longer time. I was tormented by Lillitu for much of my time in the end, and met LordVoryn of Libertas. He helped free me, but I lost my diamond gear.§0
§0~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Around a day or so later, I decided that some of
#- the things Folters said, about joining the dark side sounded cool and profitable, and so I offered him a deal: Twenty Diamonds and I would become a mole for Titan. However, my consience got in my way and I hatched a different plan, where I would take the 
#- diamonds and run off, and continue to side with the World Police. Due to a mistell I ended up revealling that I was trying to scam Folters, and he uploaded the conversation to reddit. Images can be seen here: §0imgur.com/a/srdi3§0
§0~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
#- Due to him posting the images without the part about the scamming, for some reason I came up with the idea that Hantzu was slandering me, and that I was going to be pearled by the World Police. I entered the end with the last of my diamond swords, and 
#- tried to confront Hantzu. I found Hantzu's alt WhoIsYou outside La Paz, and Hantzu in La Paz. I saw the idea of a player on two accounts at once as impossible, so I assumed something was up. As I started ranting at Han, soon people in The End started
#- saying that Folters isn't Hantzu. I soon realised that I had been very foolish, but before I could come to my senses I killed WhoIsYou, and HanTzu came out of La Paz and killed me. This ecounter was filmed by the criminal thief Jackjw01.
#- The video can be found here: §0youtube.com/watch?v=CRPUkvXxyNU§0
§0~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ I became the laughing stock of Civcraft for a few days, especially when I asked Folters for reperations, but I learned not to believe everything people say.§0
§0The End.
#- 